<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">Prayer for the Twenty-Two</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Jun 22, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
On average, twenty-two veterans commit suicide every day.
</p>

 <p>
God of peace,
</p>

 <p>
We pray for those who <br></br>
bear the scars of war, <br></br>
both visible and invisible, <br></br>
for wounds that cannot be seen <br></br>
are no less painful to bear, <br></br>
and peace is but a distant dream <br></br>
when the war is within oneâ€™s own soul.
</p>

 <p>
Give them the courage to speak, <br></br>
and give us to grace to listen.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


